// Markdown (ai-ui display)
// AI-UI component that renders markdown content with syntax highlighting,
// GFM tables, and full custom component overrides for all standard elements.
// Detects system dark mode for code block theme selection.

The "p" element override detects when children contain block-level elements
(div, pre, or function components with inline=false) and renders as <div>
instead of <p> to avoid invalid HTML nesting.

FUNCTION Markdown(content, allowHtml, strikethrough, tables, codeHighlight, ariaLabel) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Detects isDarkMode from window.matchMedia.
  Renders ReactMarkdown with remark-gfm (when tables=true) and a full
  components map overriding: h1-h6, p (with block-child detection), blockquote,
  ul, ol, li, table, thead, tbody, tr, th, td, code (syntax-highlighted blocks
  via react-syntax-highlighter using atomOneDark/atomOneLight, or inline code),
  a (opens in new tab), img, hr, del.
  skipHtml=!allowHtml.
  Wrapped in a max-h-96 scrollable container.
